ۡتِيلٗا"], "reading": [], "ortho": [0, 1, 3, 4, 5], "abuamr_only": [], "en": "So remember the name of thy Lord and devote thyself with a complete devotion", "wbw": [["And remember", "wa-udh'kuri"], ["(the) name", "is'ma"], ["(of) your Lord", "rabbika"], ["and devote yourself", "watabattal"], ["to Him", "ilayhi"], ["(with) devotion", "tabtīlan"]]}, {"hafs_aya": 9, "warsh_aya": 8, "abuamr_aya": 9, "hafs": ["رَّبُّ", "ٱلۡمَشۡرِقِ", "وَٱلۡمَغۡرِبِ", "لَآ", "إِلَٰهَ", "إِلَّا", "هُوَ", "فَٱتَّخِذۡهُ", "وَكِيلٗا"], "warsh": ["رَّبُّ", "اُ۬لْمَشْرِقِ", "وَالْمَغْرِبِۖ", "لَآ", "إِلَٰهَ", "إِلَّا", "هُوَۖ", "فَاتَّخِذْهُ", "وَكِيلاٗۖ"], "abuamr": ["رَّبُّ", "اُ۬لۡمَشۡرِقِ", "وَاَلۡمَغۡرِبِ", "لَآ", "إِلَٰهَ", "إِلَّا", "هُوَ", "فَاَتَّخِذۡهُ", "وَكِيلٗا"], "reading": [], "ortho": [1, 2, 6, 7, 8], "abuamr_only": [], "en": "Lord of the East and the West; there is no Allah save Him; so choose thou Him alone for thy defender", "wbw": [["(The) Lord", "rabbu"], ["(of) the east", "l-mashriqi"], ["and the west", "wal-maghribi"], ["(there is) no", "lā"], ["god", "ilāha"], ["except", "illā"], ["Him", "huwa"], ["so take Him", "fa-ittakhidh'hu"], ["(as) Disposer of Affairs", "wakīlan"]]}, {"hafs_aya": 10, "warsh_aya": 9, "abuamr_aya": 10, "hafs": ["وَٱصۡبِرۡ", "عَلَىٰ", "مَا", "يَقُولُونَ", "وَٱهۡجُرۡهُمۡ", "هَجۡرٗا", "جَمِيلٗا"], "warsh": ["وَاصْبِرْ", "عَلَىٰ", "مَا", "يَقُولُونَۖ", "وَاهْجُرْهُمْ", "هَجْراٗ", "جَمِيلاٗۖ"], "abuamr": ["وَاَصۡبِرۡ", "عَلَىٰ", "مَا", "يَقُولُونَ", "وَاَهۡجُرۡهُمۡ", "هَجۡرٗا", "جَمِيلٗا"], "reading": [], "ortho": [0, 3, 4, 5, 6], "abuamr_only": [], "en": "And bear with patience what they utter, and part from them with a fair leave-taking", "wbw": [["And be patient", "wa-iṣ'bir"], ["over", "ʿalā"], ["what", "mā"], ["they say", "yaqūlūna"], ["and avoid them", "wa-uh'jur'hum"], ["an avoidance", "hajran"], ["gracious", "jamīlan"]]}, {"hafs_aya": 11, "warsh_aya": 10, "abuamr_aya": 11, "hafs": ["وَذَرۡنِي", "وَٱلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ", "أُوْلِي", "ٱلنَّعۡمَةِ", "و